  "title": "Looking for Locum Speech Therapist (3-5 Days/Week) #HGAT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Assess and treat speech, language, and communication disorders</li><li>Create and implement therapy plans</li><li>Collaborate with families and professionals</li><li>Educate patients on speech improvement techniques</li><li>Maintain accurate records of treatment and progress</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as required</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Degree in Speech and Language Therapy and registered with AHPC</li><li>Minimum 1 year of experience in speech therapy</li><li>Minimum commitment: 3-6 months</li></ul><p>Interested candidates can write in to Ann at <a href=\"mailto:pharma@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">pharma@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p><br />\n<strong>Ann Goh Xin Ting</strong><br /><strong>\nR1875289</strong></p><p><strong>Recruit\nExpress Pte Ltd</strong><br /><strong>\nE.A License: 99C4599</strong></p>",
